---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Breadcrumb from "../../components/Breadcrumb.astro";
import ServiceCard from "../../components/ServiceCard.astro";
import CTAStrip from "../../components/CTAStrip.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Web Design & SEO Services | doticrosst"
  description="Website design, local SEO, and ongoing support for small businesses. Specialist division for hairdressers and barbers."
>
  <section class="pt-12 pb-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: "Home", href: "/" }, { label: "Services" }]} />
      <div class="mt-4 max-w-2xl">
        <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold text-charcoal sm:text-5xl">Web Design & SEO for Small Businesses</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          We design and build websites for small businesses, with a specialist
          division dedicated to the hair and barber industry. Every site is fast,
          mobile-first, and built to rank.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-32 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <ServiceCard
          title="Website Design & SEO"
          description="Clean, fast websites with local SEO baked in. We build on static architecture so your site loads instantly and ranks well. Suitable for any small business."
          href="/services/website-design/"
          icon='<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>'
        />
        <ServiceCard
          title="Hair & Barber Specialists"
          description="A dedicated division for hairdressers and barbers. We know the industry, the workflows, and what your clients expect when they search for you online."
          href="/services/hair-barber/"
          icon='<svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M6 3v18"/><path d="M18 3v18"/><path d="M6 8c4 0 4 4 8 4s4-4 8-4"/><path d="M6 16c4 0 4-4 8-4s4 4 8 4"/></svg>'
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why these services -->
  <section class="py-32 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-charcoal">Web design and SEO that works for small businesses</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          Most small businesses are stuck with either a DIY website built on Wix or Squarespace
          that loads slowly and ranks poorly, or they paid an agency thousands for a WordPress
          site that needs constant plugin updates and monthly hosting fees. Neither option is
          good enough. Our web design and SEO services give you a third option: a hand-coded,
          static-first website that loads in under a second, costs nothing to host, and is
          built to rank in local search from day one.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          Every service we offer is designed around one goal: making your website bring in
          more customers. That means fast page speeds, mobile-first design for the 70% of
          visitors who arrive on their phone, local SEO targeting the searches your customers
          actually make, and clear content that converts browsers into buyers. We do not sell
          services you do not need. If your business would benefit more from a strong Google
          Business Profile than a blog, we will tell you that upfront.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-gray-500">
          We also run a specialist division for hairdressers and barbers because we know
          the industry inside out. But every small business we work with gets the same
          attention to detail, the same fast build times, and the same commitment to results.
          Our services are built for businesses that want a website that earns its keep, not
          just one that exists.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What every site includes -->
  <section class="py-32 border-t border-gray-100">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal sm:text-4xl">The standard, raised</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-14 grid max-w-3xl grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
        {[
          "Mobile-first responsive design",
          "Page speed optimisation",
          "Local SEO setup",
          "SSL / HTTPS included",
          "Google Analytics integration",
          "Contact form with spam protection",
          "Social media linking",
          "Accessibility best practices",
          "Sitemap & robots.txt",
          "Ongoing support options",
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 bg-white px-5 py-4 shadow-sm">
            <span class="mt-1 block h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-charcoal flex-shrink-0"></span>
            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-charcoal">{item}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTAStrip
    heading="Ready to grow your business online?"
    text="Fill in our scoping form and get a clear quote within one working day. No obligation."
    buttonText="Start Your Project"
    buttonHref="/get-started/"
  />
</BaseLayout>
